text.tspan: Output: Lifted PDDL (= discrete dynamics parameterized by objects)
To generate a lifted PDDL from the scratch (no human supervision),
the system should find the following symbols (discrete variables) unsupervised:
PDDL-compatible, white-box lifted descriptions of actions
Lifted action description should be generalized over objects, therefore
Since all symbols are learned unsupervised, they have anonymous names
They do not learn next(x, y): they learn p1(x, y)
They do not learn move(x, y): they learn a3(x, y)
The network must be size-invariant and permutation-invariant
A boolean array of size 1 + O + O2 + ... + ON
